              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>This dashboard reflects observable regulatory exposure in public records. It does not directly measure clinical risk, device safety, or manufacturer quality. Reporting intensity may vary substantially across device categories.</run>
